Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.98,0:00:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}We really are going to surprise her\Nby waking her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.51,0:00:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Good morning, Nana!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.35,0:00:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Nana!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.15,0:00:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Detectives.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.07,0:01:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I am sorry to hear about your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.67,0:01:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Mr Tezuka, today...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.47,0:01:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}About my wife, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.83,0:01:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I will do anything to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.55,0:01:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Why don't you come up?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.59,0:01:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}- Yes.\N- No. We're here for something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.99,0:01:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}We'll visit you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.95,0:01:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.11,0:01:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Please call me if anything happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.39,0:01:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.96,0:01:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Mr Mizuki, you said we would come\Nto talk to Shota Tezuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.50,0:01:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I feel sorry for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.52,0:01:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}He just came home\Nfrom his wife's funeral!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.08,0:01:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Not legally married, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.52,0:01:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Don't talk about them like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.88,0:01:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Shota Tezuka has found\Ntoo many murder victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.72,0:01:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}When you said he was suspicious,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.76,0:01:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}l thought you were right,\Nwhich was unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.40,0:02:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I just lost the motivation.\NThe man seems nice, doesn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.91,0:02:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Detectives don't judge a book\Nby its cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.79,0:02:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Let's go back
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.99,0:02:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}and check everything again by\Nassuming that Shota Tezuka
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.43,0:02:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}was the culprit in the cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.31,0:02:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.60,0:02:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Let's smile together\Nand we'll overcome everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.86,0:02:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Yeah. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.16,0:03:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Say that you want a coffee maker\Nthat costs 5,800 yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.96,0:03:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.88,0:03:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I want to share everything\Nin our home with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.19,0:03:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}Make fried pork with tartar sauce\Nnext time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.51,0:03:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}What about fried beef?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.55,0:03:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}That too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.63,0:03:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}So good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}I miss you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.26,0:03:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}"Your Turn to Kill Special"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.55,0:04:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397\i1}The match is over if you give up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.40,0:04:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}"The account is locked"
