Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.03,0:05:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}"Password incorrect"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.59,0:05:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx346\fscy397}The day that we started dating.
